attr.title: Crunky's Fun Rager
attr.desc: In Crunky's Fun Rager, you play as Crunky, a bouncy energetic bunny seeking revenge against the mischievous Crunko Pops. Your goal? Keep Crunky hopping, dodge obstacles, and defeat enemies. Jump on Crunko Pops to squash them or collect power-ups that grant Crunky unique abilities.
attr.inst: Download the game on Itch.io (https://carsonk.itch.io/crunkys-fun-rager) and copy the SuperCrunky-v1.0.0-drm-free.zip into the assets folder.
attr.inst_md: Download the game on [Itch.io](https://carsonk.itch.io/crunkys-fun-rager) and copy the `SuperCrunky-v1.0.0-drm-free.zip` into the `assets` folder.
